        "ENG_name": "Gnomish Magic Resistance",
        "name": "侏儒魔法抗性",
        "type": "entries",
        "entries": [
          "你在进行对抗法术的智力，感知和魅力豁免时具有优势。"
        ]
      },
      {
        "ENG_name": "Svirfneblin Camouflage",
        "name": "斯涅布力伪装",
        "type": "entries",
        "entries": [
